    "en": {
      "title": "Two injured in a shooting in Negombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police Media Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Mr. Nihal Talduwa said that two persons who came on a motorcycle shot at two persons who were waiting near the Negombo Court and ran away.",
        "The two persons injured in the incident have been admitted to the Negombo General Hospital",
        "The two persons are between the ages of 40 and 51, residents of Katana Demanhandia area."
      ],
